query TTT
SELECT name, type, comment FROM objects WHERE schema = 'mz_internal' AND object = 'mz_source_statistics' ORDER BY position
----
id  text  The‚ź†ID‚ź†of‚ź†the‚ź†source.‚ź†Corresponds‚ź†to‚ź†`mz_catalog.mz_sources.id`.
replica_id  text  The‚ź†ID‚ź†of‚ź†a‚ź†replica‚ź†running‚ź†the‚ź†source.‚ź†Corresponds‚ź†to‚ź†`mz_catalog.mz_cluster_replicas.id`.
messages_received  uint8  The‚ź†number‚ź†of‚ź†messages‚ź†the‚ź†source‚ź†has‚ź†received‚ź†from‚ź†the‚ź†external‚ź†system.‚ź†Messages‚ź†are‚ź†counted‚ź†in‚ź†a‚ź†source‚ź†type-specific‚ź†manner.‚ź†Messages‚ź†do‚ź†not‚ź†correspond‚ź†directly‚ź†to‚ź†updates:‚ź†some‚ź†messages‚ź†produce‚ź†multiple‚ź†updates,‚ź†while‚ź†other‚ź†messages‚ź†may‚ź†be‚ź†coalesced‚ź†into‚ź†a‚ź†single‚ź†update.
bytes_received  uint8  The‚ź†number‚ź†of‚ź†bytes‚ź†the‚ź†source‚ź†has‚ź†read‚ź†from‚ź†the‚ź†external‚ź†system.‚ź†Bytes‚ź†are‚ź†counted‚ź†in‚ź†a‚ź†source‚ź†type-specific‚ź†manner‚ź†and‚ź†may‚ź†or‚ź†may‚ź†not‚ź†include‚ź†protocol‚ź†overhead.
updates_staged  uint8  The‚ź†number‚ź†of‚ź†updates‚ź†(insertions‚ź†plus‚ź†deletions)‚ź†the‚ź†source‚ź†has‚ź†written‚ź†but‚ź†not‚ź†yet‚ź†committed‚ź†to‚ź†the‚ź†storage‚ź†layer.
updates_committed  uint8  The‚ź†number‚ź†of‚ź†updates‚ź†(insertions‚ź†plus‚ź†deletions)‚ź†the‚ź†source‚ź†has‚ź†committed‚ź†to‚ź†the‚ź†storage‚ź†layer.
records_indexed  uint8  The‚ź†number‚ź†of‚ź†individual‚ź†records‚ź†indexed‚ź†in‚ź†the‚ź†source‚ź†envelope‚ź†state.
bytes_indexed  uint8  The‚ź†number‚ź†of‚ź†bytes‚ź†stored‚ź†in‚ź†the‚ź†source's‚ź†internal‚ź†index,‚ź†if‚ź†any.
rehydration_latency  interval  The‚ź†amount‚ź†of‚ź†time‚ź†it‚ź†took‚ź†for‚ź†the‚ź†source‚ź†to‚ź†rehydrate‚ź†its‚ź†internal‚ź†index,‚ź†if‚ź†any,‚ź†after‚ź†the‚ź†source‚ź†last‚ź†restarted.
snapshot_records_known  uint8  The‚ź†size‚ź†of‚ź†the‚ź†source's‚ź†snapshot,‚ź†measured‚ź†in‚ź†number‚ź†of‚ź†records.‚ź†See‚ź†below‚ź†to‚ź†learn‚ź†what‚ź†constitutes‚ź†a‚ź†record.
snapshot_records_staged  uint8  The‚ź†number‚ź†of‚ź†records‚ź†in‚ź†the‚ź†source's‚ź†snapshot‚ź†that‚ź†Materialize‚ź†has‚ź†read.‚ź†See‚ź†below‚ź†to‚ź†learn‚ź†what‚ź†constitutes‚ź†a‚ź†record.
