lag  interval  The‚ź†amount‚ź†of‚ź†time‚ź†the‚ź†object's‚ź†write‚ź†frontier‚ź†lags‚ź†behind‚ź†wallclock‚ź†time.
occurred_at  timestamp‚ź†with‚ź†time‚ź†zone  Wall-clock‚ź†timestamp‚ź†at‚ź†which‚ź†the‚ź†event‚ź†occurred.

query TTT
SELECT name, type, comment FROM objects WHERE schema = 'mz_internal' AND object = 'mz_wallclock_global_lag_history' ORDER BY position
