object_id  text  The‚ź†ID‚ź†of‚ź†the‚ź†table,‚ź†source,‚ź†materialized‚ź†view,‚ź†index,‚ź†or‚ź†sink.‚ź†Corresponds‚ź†to‚ź†`mz_objects.id`.
lag  interval  The‚ź†minimum‚ź†wallclock‚ź†lag‚ź†observed‚ź†for‚ź†the‚ź†object‚ź†during‚ź†the‚ź†minute.
